$ ----------------------------------------------------------------------
$ Cantilever beam -- SOL 103 (Normal Modes)
$
$ Same geometry / material as cantilever_beam.bdf. Extracts the first
$ five modes via Lanczos (EIGRL). Useful for verifying MYSTRAN's
$ eigenvalue extractor and the Animation Timeline workflow on a small
$ deck.
$
$ Analytical first bending frequency (Euler-Bernoulli):
$   f_1 = (1.875)^2 / (2*pi*L^2) * sqrt(E*I / (rho*A))
$   for L=10, I=0.0833 in^4, E=9.9e6, rho=0.098 lbm/in^3 / 386.4 in/s^2
$   rho_mass = 0.098 / 386.4 = 2.537e-4 slinch/in^3
$   f_1 ~ 81 Hz   (Mode 1 cycles should land around this)
$
$ The MIN4T QUAD shell formulation is not used (this is a beam-only
$ model); SOLLIB / QUAD4TYP PARAMs that Node Runner injects are
$ harmless here.
$ ----------------------------------------------------------------------
SOL 103
CEND
TITLE = Cantilever beam - SOL 103 (normal modes)
SUBCASE 1
  METHOD = 100
  SPC = 1
  DISPLACEMENT(PRINT,PLOT) = ALL
BEGIN BULK
$
PARAM,WTMASS,2.588-3
$
$ -------- Material --------
MAT1           1  9.9+6          .33    .098
$
$ -------- Property --------
PBARL,1,1,,BAR
,1.,1.
$
$ -------- Nodes --------
GRID           1              0.      0.      0.
GRID           2              1.      0.      0.
GRID           3              2.      0.      0.
GRID           4              3.      0.      0.
GRID           5              4.      0.      0.
GRID           6              5.      0.      0.
GRID           7              6.      0.      0.
GRID           8              7.      0.      0.
GRID           9              8.      0.      0.
GRID          10              9.      0.      0.
GRID          11             10.      0.      0.
$
$ -------- Elements --------
CBAR           1       1       1       2      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           2       1       2       3      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           3       1       3       4      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           4       1       4       5      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           5       1       5       6      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           6       1       6       7      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           7       1       7       8      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           8       1       8       9      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           9       1       9      10      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          10       1      10      11      0.      1.      0.
$
$ -------- Constraint (root clamped) --------
SPC1           1  123456       1
$
$ -------- Eigenvalue extraction (first 5 modes, Lanczos) --------
$ EIGRL,SID,V1,V2,ND
EIGRL        100      0.   2000.       5
$
ENDDATA
